I think you're pretty close, maybe try with the "if not loop.last" param like this it could work:
```
[
    {% for entity in input %}
        {
            "start_offset": {{ entity.start_offset }},
            "end_offset": {{ entity.end_offset}},
            "label": "{{ entity.label }}"
        }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
]
```

